The Board issued the following press releases on Friday announcing the
comment period deadline of August 15, 2001 for Regulation W and for the
Interim Final Rules. For those who may be searching for the Federal Register
Notice, the regulations have not yet been printed.  The Board sent the
regulations to the Federal Register last week and expects they will be
printed on either May 10, 2001 or May 11, 2001.  Please do not hesitate to
call if you have any questions.  Many thanks!

